CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. A18 reads: "Salute For Nancy - The Ida J. Brannen Wesleyan Service Guild of Warren Methodist Church presented a "This Is Your Life" program in honor of one of its members, Miss Nancy H. Lee, in recognition of achievement made in religious and social endeavors, as well as in job status. Left to right :Mrs. Dorothy G. Moore, narrator; Mrs. Shadie Crosland, president; Miss Lee, the honoree, and Noraella Brown, chairman. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Ida J. Brannen Wesleyan Service Guild of Warren Methodist Church Dorothy G. Moore, Shadie Crosland, Nancy H. Lee holding "This is Your Life" book, and Noraella Brown, posed in domestic interior with television
